  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t习近平和中共把中国经济搞的一团糟，几年来底层的收入停滞，三年疫情更是把中国人当畜牲一样关进猪圈。河南银行以及各种行业爆雷，中共不是想着解决问题，而是如何镇压人民，封锁消息。甘肃地震和各地水灾更是显露出中共基建的假面具。<br/>\r\n中共只不过搞了几个东南亚免签（不用想又是出卖各种利益换来），立马就让<mark>支那猪</mark>高潮了，恨不得全家下跪，把母亲和妻子奉献给习近平表达忠心<br/>\r\n不管这人是<mark>支那猪</mark>还是五毛，管理员还是处理了吧。这种低能贱狗我看着都觉得恶心<br/>\n<b><i>说起来，品葱的中共五毛新号怎么越来越多了，看来中共宁愿给水军钱也不愿意给底层钱呀。真是太美妙了</i></b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGIxYTY0NzI4NTBlYzE0NjZmZjM4LnBuZz93aWR0aD00MjAmaGVpZ2h0PTg2OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0b1a6472850ec1466ff38.png?width=420&amp;height=868\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0b1a6472850ec1466ff38.png?width=420&amp;height=868\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0b1a6472850ec1466ff38.png?width=420&amp;height=868\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGY5NDljNjNjMjg5MzJlZjAyMmRiLnBuZz93aWR0aD00MjAmaGVpZ2h0PTg2OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/df949c63c28932ef022db.png?width=420&amp;height=868\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/df949c63c28932ef022db.png?width=420&amp;height=868\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/df949c63c28932ef022db.png?width=420&amp;height=868\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmZlMGQ2YWUyNGRlMWRiMWZiMzcyLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD01NzM\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bfe0d6ae24de1db1fb372.png?width=1080&amp;height=573\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bfe0d6ae24de1db1fb372.png?width=1080&amp;height=573\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bfe0d6ae24de1db1fb372.png?width=1080&amp;height=573\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDNkNTUwZmZlYWYyOTZmZjlkZDMwLnBuZz93aW